{"tid":478304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想祝福前度?","createTime":"2017-11-24T02:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T03:30:33.000Z","uid":76010,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b46d2baa09ef5fba577967c0431991d01812e81","tid":478304,"uid":76010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"親愛的前度:<br />\n<br />\n之前你比我老死溝咗, 好唔開心, 仲有啲憎佢。不過見到你地差唔多一齊咗一年幾，又咁開心。我決定選擇放低你。而且，我都要多謝你男朋友教識我咩叫朋友妻，咪走雞。將來你同佢散咗，我都可能會溝番你(當你係臭雞黎)。祝你地幸福快樂。<br />\n<br />\n浪子兄上.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搶兄弟女朋友的人應全部仆街死</span></span>"},{"pid":"07ab0cba81465697e491e2cac3ab2472bd469997","tid":478304,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"唔犯法我會juk佢食屎"},{"pid":"a33fc7cab1c063fb14e2665e3865b399198b5e81","tid":478304,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"恭祝你生日撼穿個頭，<br />\n慶賀你死埋老豆；<br />\n年年都要乞食，<br />\n歲歲都要楂兜，<br />\n恭喜你，恭喜你。"},{"pid":"ce571b3eb2b457e1b5f943cdb7676bf231535164","tid":478304,"uid":76010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔犯法我會juk佢食屎</blockquote><br />\n我條女都食，我啲屎點會唔食"},{"pid":"21d8449e75adff2a3583c45905fb0ee2b90a690a","tid":478304,"uid":93892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"祝佢繼續比帽人帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa201366160981d9bed9d8175683aa89e91a86f","tid":478304,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭祝你生日撼穿個頭，<br />\n慶賀你死埋老豆；<br />\n年年都要乞食，<br />\n歲歲都要楂兜，<br />\n恭喜你，恭喜你。</blockquote><br />\n你都重係咁幼稚"},{"pid":"9ca81f2717e7a3244e59b88106b1bc3fcece457a","tid":478304,"uid":158273,"like":0,"dislike":0,